name: Ingegärd
description: She's intrepid, affectionate, generous and perhaps a little too timid. This isn't surprising considering for someone with his position.

name: Gudfinna
description: She was born in a decent family in an important port. She lived free of worries until she was about 14 years old, but at that point things changed.

name: Freystein
description: He's funny, driven, reliable and perhaps a little too pompous. Which isn't out of the ordinary for someone with his position.

name: Ingifast
description: He is currently searching for a higher purpose. He feels like there's more than what we get to know in this world. Luckily he has great parents to support him.

name: Svartbrand
description: While haunted by memories of the past, he now works a small job with low pay. By doing so, he hopes to start life over on a good note and finally find friends he has never had.
